main event: A round, luminous colored object with a tail was sighted at an angle to earth 3000 feet up in North Bend, Oregon.
interesting points: The object was described as very bright green and round with a tail., The sighting lasted for a few seconds., Witnesses were driving a car uphill and had a direct line of vision to the object., The object might have fallen into the water., Conditions were reported as having been rainy but cleared, with small patches of fog present.
sighted object: round luminous colored object with a tail
